Package chess.domain.board

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BetterPiece
    This represents chess pieces.
    ChessBoard
    This class is responsible for keeping track of the current situation on board.
    ChessBoardCopier
    This class is used to make copies of ChessBoards with method copy as well as make two chessboards deeply equal or undo a move by making its start point and end point equal to backup.
    Square
    Square class is responsible for keeping track of its location and possible piece situated on it.

    Klass
